Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.27,0:23:07.34,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:13.26,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.44,0:23:19.13,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:21.53,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.70,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:28.54,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.52,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:36.10,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:39.59,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.66,0:23:43.46,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.62,0:23:46.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
